{
  "text": "Intravitreal Injection. Intravitreal injections were performed following established protocols [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We injected 1 μg of miR-150 mimics (Ambion) using a 33-gauge needle behind the limbus of the eye, and the contralateral eye of the same animal was injected with an equal amount of negative control mimics.",
